<!DOCTYPE html>
<!--[if IE 9]>         <html class="ie9 no-focus" lang="en"> <![endif]-->
<!--[if gt IE 9]><!--> <html class="no-focus" lang="en"> <!--<![endif]-->
<html>
  <head>
    <% include ./config/header_landing.ejs %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <% include ./config/nav_landing.ejs %>
    <header class="masthead text-center text-white d-flex">
      <div class="container my-auto">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-10 mx-auto">
            <h1 class="text-uppercase">
              <strong>필요 없는 티켓과 구하고 싶은 티켓, 이젠 경매로 사고파세요!</strong>
            </h1>
            <hr>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
            <p class="text-faded mb-5">티켓온은 본인에게는 필요가 없거나 안쓰는 티켓을 필요한 사람에게 팔 수 있는 경매 방식의 서비스입니다.
               경매를 통해 티켓을 원하는 가격선에서 쟁취하세요!</p>
              <a class="btn-radius btn-primary btn-xl js-scroll-trigger" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#loginModal">로그인 하기</a>
              <a class="btn-radius btn-primary btn-xl js-scroll-trigger" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#registerModal">회원가입 하기</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>
    <% include ./auth/login.ejs %>
    <% include ./auth/register.ejs %>
    <% include ./auth/findID.ejs %>
    <% include ./auth/findPwd.ejs %>
    <% include ./config/footer_landing.ejs %>

    <section id="services">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
            <h2 class="section-heading">티켓온 소개</h2>
            <hr class="my-4">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 text-center">
            <div class="service-box mt-5 mx-auto">
              <i class="fa fa-4x fa-ticket text-primary mb-3 sr-icons"></i>
              <h3 class="mb-3">티켓 등록</h3>
              <p class="text-muted mb-0">자신에게는 필요없는 티켓을 경매로 등록해보세요.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 text-center">
            <div class="service-box mt-5 mx-auto">
              <i class="fa fa-4x fa-legal text-primary mb-3 sr-icons"></i>
              <h3 class="mb-3">입찰/낙찰</h3>
              <p class="text-muted mb-0">자신에게 필요한 티켓은 입찰하여 낙찰해보세요.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 text-center">
            <div class="service-box mt-5 mx-auto">
              <i class="fa fa-4x fa-credit-card text-primary mb-3 sr-icons"></i>
              <h3 class="mb-3">결제</h3>
              <p class="text-muted mb-0">낙찰받은 티켓은 결제해야합니다.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 text-center">
            <div class="service-box mt-5 mx-auto">
              <i class="fa fa-4x fa-paper-plane text-primary mb-3 sr-icons"></i>
              <h3 class="mb-3">티켓 수령</h3>
              <p class="text-muted mb-0">모든 과정이 완료되면 티켓을 수령합니다.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="bg-primary">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto text-center">
            <h2 class="section-heading text-white">티켓온 문의</h2>
            <hr class="light my-4">
            <p class="text-faded mb-5">티켓온을 이용하면서 궁금증이나 어려움이 있으신가요? 아래 번호나 메일로 문의해주세요. <br> 저희는 항상 기다리고 있답니다.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-4 ml-auto text-center">
            <i class="fa fa-phone fa-3x mb-3 sr-contact text-white"></i>
            <p class="text-faded">010-1234-5678</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-4 mr-auto text-center">
            <i class="fa fa-envelope-o fa-3x mb-3 sr-contact text-white"></i>
            <p class="text-faded">ticketon@ticketon.com</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </body>
</html>
